---
title: Fried Rice with Honey-Soy Ginger Beef
description: There are few things as easily assembled and uniquely satisfying as fried rice. We’re taking it back to basics with this traditional dish and topping it off with perfectly flavoursome marinated beef.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b7219b930006c339e0cbac2-7c4ba2aa.jpg
